  "body": "**Steps:**\r\n1. Open chat\r\n2. Trigger app asking for permission to Camera/microphone (by tapping on camera/microphone icon)\r\n3. Select allow 'Only this time option'\r\n4. Try to trigger app asking for permission once again and observe the result\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** permissions are not asked. App behaves as if \"While using the app\" option was selected during previous permission asking. In Android system permissions settings 'Ask every time' option is selected. \r\n\r\n**Expected result:** permissions are asked every time if allow 'Only this time' option has been previously selected. \r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/191247353-bc2551cb-5eaf-49df-b712-dba943d18b41.mp4\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly. 1.19, 1.20\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
